commit.message: Bumped version to 0.2.1.
Switched CI from travis.ci to github actions.
Updated deps.
Bump version to 0.2.0.
Extend isstds and isuts by defaults if too short.
Use spec in RFC 8536.
CI includes latest of each major version in the GHC 8 series.
New .travis.yml.
Limit travis CI to GHC >= 8.
Bump version to 0.1.9.
Add Semigroup instance for GHC >= 8.4.
Fix name of travis CI script.
Added travis CI.
Update copyright.
Bumped version to 0.1.8.
